    • Method Detail

      • modelChanged

        void modelChanged(OrderBookModelListener.Change change)
        Called after a change has been made to an OrderBookModel.

        Note, that the change object object currently provides only information about the source of the change (what model has changed) and does not actually provide information about what orders in the model has changed. The model has to be queried using lists of buy and sell orders to get the new set of active orders in the book.

        Warning: Change object can be reused and can become invalid when another change occurs on the model. It is not safe to use this change object on a different thread from the listener's thread.

        Parameters:
        change - an object representing the change.
